id: It looks like the impostor has done some events. These will be displayed on your left panel. Review them and then access the room again.
str: It looks like the impostor has done some events. These will be displayed on your left panel. Review them and then access the room again.

id: Remember to keep the door locked with the latch. If you don't, the dolls can come out, alter your tests, and even kill you.
str: Remember to keep the door locked with the latch. If you don't, the dolls can come out, alter your tests, and even kill you.

id: This is the dolls' room. Here you will see what they have done while you slept. Take a look at them, and then let's go back to the room.
str: This is the dolls' room. Here you will see what they have done while you slept. Take a look at them, and then let's go back to the room.

id: Let's go back to the panel and start weeding out suspects who don't match our evidence.
str: Let's go back to the panel and start weeding out suspects who don't match our evidence.

id: You have all the clues and all the information about the dolls, but this is completely random for each doll.
str: You have all the clues and all the information about the dolls, but this is completely random for each doll.

id: We only have 3 left. Let's go to the room to see who has moved and who has been moved.
str: We only have 3 left. Let's go to the room to see who has moved and who has been moved.

id: You've made it through the tutorial, you know the basics! To finish the tutorial, go to bed and sleep. You will go to your safe zone. Use the computer to start a game!
str: You've made it through the tutorial, you know the basics! To finish the tutorial, go to bed and sleep. You will go to your safe zone. Use the computer to start a game!

id: You are the guardian of dolls, one of them is alive and intends to kill you. You must discover which one it is before 09:00.
str: You are the guardian of dolls, one of them is alive and intends to kill you. You must discover which one it is before 09:00.

id: Perfect, we have 5 suspects left. Let's go to sleep again.
str: Perfect, we have 5 suspects left. Let's go to sleep again.

id: Random but endless mode, you have a 3-minute timer to fix the case and there is a leaderboard of leaders
str: Random but endless mode, you have a 3-minute timer to fix the case and there is a leaderboard of leaders

id: The standard difficulty for each player, all clues will be made at 08:00, you have the option to see the names of the dolls and the list of actions of the imposter
str: The standard difficulty for each player, all clues will be made at 08:00, you have the option to see the names of the dolls and the list of actions of the imposter

id: It's the last hour. We only have this chance to find out. Let's go to the room.
str: It's the last hour. We only have this chance to find out. Let's go to the room.

id: You will have a detective role in which you will have to determine, based on the impostor's likes and dislikes listed on the panel to your left, what he likes and doesn't like, who his enemies, friends, loves, or hated individuals are.
str: You will have a detective role in which you will have to determine, based on the impostor's likes and dislikes listed on the panel to your left, what he likes and doesn't like, who his enemies, friends, loves, or hated individuals are.

id: Only suitable for professionals, it starts at 08:00 and only has 3 effective clues, there are no photos or aids, some of the data is hidden, you have limited access to the map
str: Only suitable for professionals, it starts at 08:00 and only has 3 effective clues, there are no photos or aids, some of the data is hidden, you have limited access to the map

id: Let's set a trap for the impostor. We already know that he likes TV and music. Turn on the lights.
str: Let's set a trap for the impostor. We already know that he likes TV and music. Turn on the lights.

id: You've broken your new record with {new} nights! of the {old} nights before!
str: You've broken your new record with {new} nights! of the {old} nights before!

id: You can try it now in PC
str: You can try it now in PC

id: You've unlocked a new extra mode!
str: You've unlocked a new extra mode!

id: Random mode but in race mode with medals
str: Random mode but in race mode with medals

id: Can you help me with a positive review?
str: Can you help me with a positive review?

id: Welcome to the refuge! This is your safe zone. Here, you can start a new game on the computer, view your collection of dolls and trophies, and also customize this place by clicking on the colour palette icon on your desktop!
str: Welcome to the refuge! This is your safe zone. Here, you can start a new game on the computer, view your collection of dolls and trophies, and also customize this place by clicking on the colour palette icon on your desktop!

id: To sleep, simply point at the bed and click on it.
str: To sleep, simply point at the bed and click on it.

id: One more step of difficulty, there are no extra clues, You can't see the names or list
str: One more step of difficulty, there are no extra clues, You can't see the names or list

id: To start, there are 20 dolls. Check them on the board and when you are ready, go to the room to meet them.
str: To start, there are 20 dolls. Check them on the board and when you are ready, go to the room to meet them.

id: Go to sleep and let's see if the clue is solved in the next hour.
str: Go to sleep and let's see if the clue is solved in the next hour.

id: It is clear that he likes blood. It could be either of the two, but check the boxes. Freddy is missing and his box is full of blood. He left this verdict for you. When you are sure, discard the candidate.
str: It is clear that he likes blood. It could be either of the two, but check the boxes. Freddy is missing and his box is full of blood. He left this verdict for you. When you are sure, discard the candidate.

id: He has fallen into our trap and turned off the lights. We can now discard all those who like the light.
str: He has fallen into our trap and turned off the lights. We can now discard all those who like the light.

id: Expert mode, you start from 06:00, there are no extra clues and no photographs
str: Expert mode, you start from 06:00, there are no extra clues and no photographs

id: As you unlock new levels, new ones will appear!
str: As you unlock new levels, new ones will appear!

id: We have Ricky on the couch and Monty at the piano, so we already have the 2 possible candidates. However, we are not going to take the 50% risk. Let's go back to the room to rule out the one that can't be and wait for his next event.
str: We have Ricky on the couch and Monty at the piano, so we already have the 2 possible candidates. However, we are not going to take the 50% risk. Let's go back to the room to rule out the one that can't be and wait for his next event.

id: You've got {new} nights, you haven't managed to beat your record of {old} nights
str: You've got {new} nights, you haven't managed to beat your record of {old} nights
